org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.common.query

Class QueryHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.common.query.QueryHandler

  • public class QueryHandler
extends Object
    Wraps a GDLHandler and adds functionality needed for query processing during graph pattern matching.
